    "7307314": {
        "Desc": "Return to the secret base",
        "Step": "Finally, all the fragments of the Amiti Device have been gathered, and you also discovered Ararycan's past. Should Royinjan be told of it, though?",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey Royinjan, we're back!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Royinjan",
                    "T": "There you are. Looks like you met the old man and found the fragments you were looking for, hmm?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Royinjan",
                    "T": "That aside, is he as tedious now as he was then? Not that I care though."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Seems you do."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You two are so alike."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Royinjan",
                    "T": "What did Amadhiah tell you? Don't believe anything he said! If he hadn't slipped back into the village the night before our adventure at sea..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Royinjan",
                    "T": "We could have been the greatest adventurers in history."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Doesn't sound very likely..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You can't change the past."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Royinjan",
                    "T": "Come on, I'm just kidding. I'm better suited to dealing in antiques."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Royinjan",
                    "T": "Even a great adventurer like my grandfather eventually went missing in their adventures. I doubt I would've stood much of a chance."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Royinjan",
                    "T": "For me, I'd be satisfied so long as there's a story to hear. So, what stories have you collected? According to our deal, the device fragments in your hands were meant to be exchanged for stories."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "About the inundated device and The Withering..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "You tell Royinjan about your search for the device fragments."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Royinjan",
                    "T": "Haha, that's a great adventure indeed. You are marvelous adventurers. If only I had been able to complete such a journey myself."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "About the fairies and the children..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "You tell Royinjan about the adventure of the Aranara and the children."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Royinjan",
                    "T": "Fairies in the forest... I've heard similar legends before, but your tale is a particularly interesting one."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Royinjan",
                    "T": "That's a good enough story for me. The fragments are yours, as we agreed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Royinjan",
                    "T": "Take them to our great researcher. He's been stressing out this entire time while you were out having your fun."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Royinjan",
                    "T": "I should get back to my shop now. I'll be quite upset if I missed out on a big sale."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wait a second, we have something else we have to do. That flower..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Amadhiah wanted you to have this."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Royinjan",
                    "T": "A flower? Seriously? At his age?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Royinjan",
                    "T": "Hold on, I think I remember this..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Have you recalled anything?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Royinjan",
                    "T": "Haha. Maybe, but then again, maybe not. Anyway, the past should stay in the past, so forget it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Royinjan",
                    "T": "But I have a feeling this flower does not belong to me, so please, return it to where it belongs. I can tell that you can see things I can't."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Royinjan",
                    "T": "He seems to have become a bit more fun than before..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Royinjan",
                    "T": "Do drop by my shop when you get the chance. Until then, farewell!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Where it belongs... The flower is yours, Ararycan."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ararycan",
                    "T": "This flower is precious. Why give it to Ararycan?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Because it belongs to you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ararycan",
                    "T": "Ararycan doesn't remember the flower, but Ararycan likes it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ararycan",
                    "T": "Ararycan cherishes this flower. Ararycan shall plant it in the garden."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We'll see you at the foot of the Great Iron Mountain. Once we get the giant machine started, we'll go get the bad guys together."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ararycan",
                    "T": "Yes, Ararycan wants to fight the bad guys with you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "That's a promise, Ararycan!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
