    "7302702": {
        "Desc": "Check the area that was hit",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey, Ararycan, what are you doing here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ararycan",
                    "T": "Ararycan has been waiting for you here since Ararycan finished sowing the flowers."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ararycan",
                    "T": "But then, something just fell off the Great Iron Mountain. It almost hit Ararycan!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh no! We're sorry, Ararycan!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ararycan",
                    "T": "Paimon doesn't have to say sorry. Ararycan is fine. Ararycan is a fast runner, so Ararycan didn't get hit."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Just glad it didn't hurt you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "The robot's severed arm must have broken the entrance to the underground ruins open. Well, at least it wasn't completely useless."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Then let's go down and have a look. Who knows what nasty things wait for us down there!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ararycan",
                    "T": "Ararycan is going with you!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7302703": {
        "Desc": "Enter the underground ruins",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "The glowing thing in there must be the Ruin Golem's Chaos Core. Y'know, the one Jazari talked about."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "It's sealed by branches and vines, but something seems to be flowing out of it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ararycan",
                    "T": "Ohh, it's the filthy stuff. Ararycan can feel it. This is what made the forest sick."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ah, some Abyss Mages seem to be up to something around those big branches. This can't be good..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon remembers Jazari said that the core's seal had been damaged. Maybe these Abyss Mages had something to do with it..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Anyway, you should go and find a place to hide, Ararycan. Let's stop them!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7302704": {
        "Desc": "Investigate the underground ruins",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Phew, it's finally over!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Well, it was a long journey, wasn't it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Let's tell this story to Jazari..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh right, if he knows about the core, he can help us apply for some funding and all that stuff."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#But Paimon's not gonna enroll in the Akademiya or anything. You aren't planning to either, right, {NICKNAME}?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Let's tell this story to grandpa Royinjan..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh yeah, and grandpa Royinjan will say, \"What an interesting story!\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Who'd know that we actually saved the forest?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Anyway, we don't know what Marana's Avatar has to do with the Abyss Order yet, but it's a good thing that we cured the forest's illness all the same."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ararycan",
                    "T": "*sob* Thank you for helping Ararycan."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You're welcome, Ararycan."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So, what do you plan to do next, Ararycan?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ararycan",
                    "T": "Ararycan will celebrate Festival Utsava. But Ararycan worries about the forest's illness."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ararycan",
                    "T": "There's a chance that the bad things that made the forest sick will come back. Ararycan needs to guard the forest."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ararycan",
                    "T": "So Ararycan will come back here after Festival Utsava."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Wow, Aranara really do have tough jobs."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "If you ever need any help, Ararycan, be sure to come to us!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ararycan",
                    "T": "Okay, Ararycan will."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hehe! Take care of yourself. We'll see each other soon!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
